- introduce L'Hôpital's rule and the intuition behind it (ratio of derivatives approximates ratio of functions near indeterminate points)
- case 1: 0/0 form at a finite limit
- case 2: 0/0 form at an infinite limit
- case 3: inf/inf form at a finite limit
- case 4: inf/inf form at an infinite limit
